---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Gallery from '../../components/Gallery.astro';
---

<Base title="AsianFox - Shoutouts - Ian Hogers" side="neutral">
  <section class="py-6">
    <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-6">
      <a href="/shoutouts" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white no-underline">â† back to shoutouts</a>
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
      <span class="text-4xl">ğŸ¨</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl text-pink-400 mb-0">AsianFox</h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-500">Artist Â· MapleStory community</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Message in the dark -->
    <div class="pixel-box pixel-box-crimson p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-center font-display tracking-wide">
        <span class="text-pink-300">If you're reading this AsianFox!</span><br>
        <span class="text-white">Reach out! How are you? ğŸ’›</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose mb-8">
      <p><strong class="text-pink-400">AsianFox</strong> was an incredible artist from another MapleStory private server. They created several art pieces - commissions that I still treasure.</p>
      <p>I even made pixel art versions of their work and streamed the drawing process. That's how much their art meant to me.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Art Gallery -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl text-pink-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="star-sprite w-5 h-5 animate-sparkle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      The Art
    </h2>

    <Gallery>
      <div class="pixel-box p-3" style="--box-color: #ec4899;">
        <img
          src="/assets/pixel-art/commissions/pepsi_transparent_by_asianfox-datirzr.png"
          alt="Pepsi Transparent by AsianFox"
          class="w-full rounded"
        />
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Pepsi (Transparent)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pixel-box p-3" style="--box-color: #ec4899;">
        <img
          src="/assets/pixel-art/commissions/screenshot__156__by_asianfox_datirvm_by_asianfox-datisbw.png"
          alt="Screenshot commission by AsianFox"
          class="w-full rounded"
        />
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Screenshot Commission</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pixel-box p-3" style="--box-color: #ec4899;">
        <img
          src="/assets/pixel-art/commissions/spoopy_woopy_by_asianfox-dau1zhy-50.png"
          alt="Spoopy Woopy by AsianFox"
          class="w-full rounded"
        />
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Spoopy Woopy</p>
      </div>
    </Gallery>

    <!-- Pixel art version -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl text-violet-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
      <img src="/assets/pixel-art/game-assets/wow_red.png" alt="" class="pixel-sprite w-5 h-5" />
      My Pixel Art Version
    </h2>

    <div class="pixel-box pixel-box-lavender p-3 sm:p-4 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
      <img
        src="/assets/pixel-art/commissions/saint-pepsi-pixel-art-version-4up.png"
        alt="Saint Pepsi - pixel art version by Ian"
        class="w-full pixel-sprite rounded"
      />
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">My pixel art version of the Saint Pepsi piece</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1 text-center italic">I streamed the drawing process - link TBD</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Other art -->
    <div class="pixel-box p-4 mb-8">
      <img
        src="/assets/pixel-art/commissions/0f7b83e676294ada15dd7dce73383638.webp"
        alt="Additional commission art"
        class="w-full rounded"
      />
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Additional piece from the collection</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pixel-divider mb-6" style="--divider-color: #ec4899;"></div>
    <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 text-center">
      AsianFox, if you ever see this - your art still means a lot. Hope you're doing well. ğŸ’›
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
